            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Gen. Imboden's Command</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"Success attend the gallant Imboden wherever his duty calls him and may he
                    be feared as much when he leaves as when he came among his admiring Pennsylvania
                    friends."</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Points the reader to the article on Imboden's success in Maryland and
                    praises the general.</summary>
                <note/>
